Disk latency per device :: Average latency for /dev/vg/lv_mysql_snapshot
UNKNOWNs: Read IO Wait time is unknown, Write IO Wait time is ...
        </div>          
        <div class="tags t-munin t-lvm">
            <a href="/questions/tagged/munin" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;munin&#39;" rel="tag">munin</a> <a href="/questions/tagged/lvm" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;lvm&#39;" rel="tag">lvm</a> 

